data.description:
SWEET HOME MONTANA just a short drive from Great Falls nestled on just over 5 ACRES, this ALL ONE LEVEL offers 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a true en-suite with a walk in closet & private bathroom that capitalizes on the views of the mountains & Square Butte! The laundry features a utility sink and room to work. 

Looking for a place WITH NO INTERIOR STAIRS? This could be the home for you! You do not have to wait to build, this home features all of the tasteful details with fresh finishes and large bright windows, it was built in 2017! 
Listed by Melissa Dascoulias
